### Sessions

### Vrati sve sesije
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sessions/GetSessions
Accept: application/json

### vrati sesije u sobi
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sessions/GetSessionsInRoom?roomId=3
Accept: application/json

### Dodaj sobu
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sessions/AddSession
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "roomId": 1,
    "aktivnostId": 2,
    "datum": "2026-03-03",
    "vremePocetka": "17:00:00",
    "vremeKraja": "18:00:00",
    "automatskiPocetak": false,
    "automatskiKraj": false,
    "automatskoKrajnjeStanje": 4
}

